cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with the task of ground terrain recognition, which involves computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of the recognition task for robot or vehicular control parameters, which suggests the category cs.RO (Robotics). The use of a deep neural network for recognition suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of supervised learning, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with the recognition of textures, which suggests the category cs.GR (Graphics).
